column4: When I try to open it from the Applications menu, it doesn't open, and it doesn't have an icon.
run 'frostwire' in a terminal and pastebin the output
the java in mutliverse will let you use frostwire just fine
Okay, my Software Sources are multiverse-enabled.
How do I download their Java?
Synaptic only shows earlier versions of Java.
type this in a terminal please:  apt-cache policy sun-java5-bin
Did that.
pastebin the output
How do i paste something from my terminal?
highlight it with your mouse then press middle click to paste in your browser
I'm using a two-button mousepad. What do I do if there's no middleclick?
you can press both buttons at the same time probably.  Or use ctrl-shift-c to copy what you selected and then paste as usual

ok when you run taht command press   3   and then enter
